  <h3>engine</h3>
  <p>For this game, I wrote a custom javascript engine. It runs in the browser, using the html <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> tag to display the game. I've learned a whole lot about game architecture since starting this project, and I sporadically get the urge to completely rewrite this in, say, C... but for now it's written in javascript :)</p>
